   "source": [
    "# DGEM — Disagreement-Guided Entropy Minimization\n",
    "**MIDL 2025 Short Paper**\n",
    "\n",
    "Semi-supervised 3D medical image segmentation on Pancreas-CT (NIH), 20% labeled.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pipeline:**\n",
    "1. Setup environment & clone repo\n",
    "2. Mount Google Drive + download data\n",
    "3. Preprocess NIfTI → H5 & generate splits\n",
    "4. Train BCP baseline (SOTA)\n",
    "5. Train DGEM (our method)\n",
    "6. Evaluate & compare\n",
    "7. Visualize loss curves + predictions\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Runtime:** GPU → Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 0. Check GPU"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "print('CUDA available:', torch.cuda.is_available())\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print('GPU:', torch.cuda.get_device_name(0))\n",
    "    print('VRAM:', round(torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_memory/1e9, 1), 'GB')\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    raise RuntimeError('No GPU found. Go to Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU')"
   ]
