   "source": [
    "## 3. Data\n",
    "\n",
    "### Option A — You already have preprocessed H5 files on Drive\n",
    "Skip to **Section 3c** (generate splits).\n",
    "\n",
    "### Option B — Download raw NIfTI from TCIA and preprocess\n",
    "1. Register at https://wiki.cancerimagingarchive.net/display/Public/Pancreas-CT\n",
    "2. Download the NBIA Data Retriever and download the dataset\n",
    "3. Upload the zipped dataset to your Drive\n",
    "4. Run the cells below to preprocess"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
